justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;><strong style=margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;><span style=margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;>宣传与赞助</span></strong></p></section><section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;>会议期间将通过会刊、网站、背景板、场内外展览展示、会场专题推介等方式进行宣传展示。热忱欢迎各单位参与赞助、同传和宣传交流，扩大影响。有意者请通过以下联系方式了解详情。</p><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;><br/></p><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;>联系人：</p><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;>刘振营 电话：13317125305 邮箱：whtran@126.com</p><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;>韦忠和 电话：13906038846 邮箱：frank@mts.cn</p><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;>朱宪超 电话：13550207555 邮箱：michael.zhu@lan-bridge.com</p><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;><br/></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;><strong style=margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;>八</strong></p></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;><strong style=margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;><span style=margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;>组委会联系方式</span></strong></p></section><section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;>联系人：吴华茜 18510246768（注册咨询）</p><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;>王海涛 13683093172（会议咨询）</p><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;>顾小放 13611174108（会议咨询）</p><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;>周莉莎 0571-87152542（酒店咨询）</p><p style=margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;>电子信箱：tr_reg@163.com</p></section></section></section></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>转自中国标准化</p>', '0', '0', '6', null, '1525655941', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `sp_notice` VALUES ('24', '国家技术标准创新基地（重庆） 关于召开2018第十六届中国ECR大会的通知', '1', '<p style=text-align:left;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>各有关单位：</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>“</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:>2018</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>年第十六届中国</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>ECR</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>大会”将于</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>2018</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>年</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:>6</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>月</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>12</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>—</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>14</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>日在重庆丽笙世嘉酒店召开。</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>&nbsp;</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>此次</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>2018 ECR</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>大会不仅为您创造了一次寻求商务合作的绝好机会，同时也为贵公司提供了一个展示实力和技术的精彩大舞台。我们热切期待着您和您的公司能在中国</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>ECR </span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>这一大舞台上赢得精彩的掌声</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>!</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>现就有关事宜通知如下：</span> </p><p style=text-indent:43px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体_GBK>一、会议时间</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>2018</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>年</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>6</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>月</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>12</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>—</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>14</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>日，６月１２日会议已报满。</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体_GBK>二、会议地点</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>重庆丽笙世嘉酒店，地址: 重庆市南岸区南滨路22号 ，电话： (023)88668888</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>。</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体_GBK>三、参会人员</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>各行业相关人员</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体_GBK>四、会议内容</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>见附件。</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正黑体_GBK>五、其他事项</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK></span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>（一）鉴于此次会议参会名额有限，请有意参会的公司和个人及时发回执，秘书处将根据您的报名时间给予参会确认。发回执到标准基地的免收会议培训费和伙食费，交通费自理；</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>（二）请将参会回执发送至479486823 @qq.com</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>；或者在标准基地官网报名：</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>https://www.xixinpt.com/home/notice/info/id/24.html</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>；</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>（三）联系方式</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>标准基地联系人：</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>邓老师，</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK> 赵老师；</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>标准基地联系电话：023—89232939，88215838；</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>标准基地电子邮箱：479486823 @qq.com；</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><br/></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK></span></p><p><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; QQ</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>群：国家标准基地会员交流 519782997；</span></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK></span><br/></p><p style=text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=text-align:left;text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>附件：1.邀请函</span></p><p style=text-align:left;text-indent:107px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>2.</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>会议议程</span></p><p style=text-align:left;text-indent:107px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>3.</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>会议回执</span></p><p style=margin-left:43px;text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=margin-left:43px;text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=margin-left:43px;text-indent:43px;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:&#39;Times>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK>国家技术标准创新基地（重庆）</span></p><p style=margin-right:57px;text-align:right;line-height:37px><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK;color:black>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2018</span><span style=font-size:21px;font-family:方正仿宋_GBK;color:black>年6月4日</span></p><p style=line-height:><img src=https://www.xixinpt.com/Public/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_doc.gif/><a style=font-size:12px; href=/ueditor/php/upload/file/20180604/1528105600217946.docx title=关于召开2018年第十六届中国ECR分论坛会议的通知.docx>关于召开2018年第十六届中国ECR分论坛会议的通知.docx</a></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '2', null, '1531282264', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `sp_notice` VALUES ('25', '于举办 2018 年第六期 “标准制修订全过程质量提升”研修班的通知', '1', '<h1 style=margin-left:181px><span style=;position:><span style=left:0px;position:absolute;left:101px;top:-132px;width:604px;height:85px> <table><tbody><tr class=firstRow><td width=604 style=word-break: break-all;><span style=position:absolute;left:0;z-index:251655676> &nbsp; 国家标准化管理委员会标准信息中心国家标准化管理委员会国家标准技术审评中心</span>&nbsp;关于举办 2018 年第六期标准制修订全过程质量提升”研修班的通知</td></tr></tbody></table></span></span></h1><p style=margin-top:1px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:><span style=font-family:>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=margin-left:36px;line-height:41px>各有关单位：</p><p style=margin-top:1px;margin-right:44px;margin-bottom:><span style=letter-spacing:>为贯彻落实 </span>2018 <span style=letter-spacing:-1px>年全国标准化工作会议提出的</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>“</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>五个全面推进</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>”</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>和</span>“<span style=letter-spacing:-0>五个突出抓好</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>”</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>工作任务，帮助广大标准化工作者</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>更好地掌握标准化法规政策和业务知识，提升标准化工作能力&nbsp; 和标准研制质量水平，结合工作实际，国家标准委标准信息中&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=letter-spacing:-3px>心</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>（</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>审评中心</span><span style=letter-spacing:-3px>）</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>决定 </span>9 <span style=letter-spacing:-0>月在重庆举办 </span>2018 <span style=letter-spacing:-1px>年第六期</span><span style=letter-spacing:>“</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>标准制修</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>订全过程质量提升</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>”</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>研修班。</span></p><p style=margin-left:78px;line-height:36px>本次研修班着重讲解新修订标准化法的立法背景和主要制</p><p style=margin-top:1px;margin-right:33px;margin-bottom:><span style=letter-spacing:-0>度调整；讲解国家标准立项指南、标准审核质量问题分析、规范、规程、指南等标准编写；讲解国家标准实施效果评价方法及操作实务，与大家一道分享中心开展标准实施效果评价的经</span><span style=letter-spacing:-1px>验和研究成果；同时针对大家关心的如何参与国际标准化活动，&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=letter-spacing:-1px>开设了《国际标准化知识》课程，热忱欢迎相关单位派员参加。&nbsp; </span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>现将具体安排通知如下：</span></p><p style=margin-top:1px;margin-right:33px;margin-bottom:><br/></p><p style=margin-top:1px;margin-right:33px;margin-bottom:><br/></p><p style=margin-top:1px;margin-right:33px;margin-bottom:>一、培训主要内容 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=margin-top:4px;margin-right:301px;margin-bottom:><span style=letter-spacing:>1.</span><span style=letter-spacing:-0>《标准化法》权威解读；</span></p><p>2.国际标准化知识；</p><p>3.国家标准立项指南与标准预研申报质量分析；</p><p>4.规范、规程、指南等标准编写要求与方法；（GB/T 20001.5～20001.7-2017）</p><p>5.标准审核质量问题及解决方案；</p><p>6.国家标准实施效果评价方法及操作实务。</p><p>注：培训日程安排开班前通过电子邮件发至报名人员。</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;二、培训时间和地点</p><p style=margin-top:1px;margin-right:97px;margin-bottom:><span style=letter-spacing:-2px>培训时间：</span><span style=letter-spacing:-1px>9</span> <span style=letter-spacing:-1px>月</span><span style=letter-spacing:-1px>19</span> <span style=letter-spacing:-2px>日 </span><span style=letter-spacing:-2px>- </span>9 <span style=letter-spacing:-1px>月</span><span style=letter-spacing:-1px>21</span> <span style=letter-spacing:-1px>日 (</span><span style=letter-spacing:-1px>9</span> <span style=letter-spacing:-1px>月</span><span style=letter-spacing:-1px>18</span> <span style=letter-spacing:-3px>日下午报到</span>) <span style=letter-spacing:-3px>培训地点：重庆</span>·金质花苑酒店</p><p style=margin-top:1px;margin-right:97px;margin-bottom:><span style=font-size: 19px;>注</span><span style=font-size: 19px; letter-spacing: 0px;>：</span><span style=font-size: 19px;>酒店联</span><span style=font-size: 19px; letter-spacing: 0px;>系</span><span style=font-size: 19px;>人陈</span><span style=font-size: 19px; letter-spacing: 0px;>经</span><span style=font-size: 19px;>理 023-89185888-8888 18680880718</span></p><p style=margin-top:4px;line-height:41px>&nbsp;三、主讲老师</p><p style=margin-top:4px;line-height:41px>有关标准化资深专家。</p><p style=margin-top:2px;line-height:41px>四、培训对象</p><p style=margin-top:1px;margin-right:44px;margin-bottom:><span style=letter-spacing:>各省市、各行业和地方从事标准化研究和管理人员；标准</span><span style=letter-spacing:-1px>化技术委员会的相关人员；各企事业单位从事标准化工作的管理人员和技术人员。</span></p><p style=margin-top:4px;line-height:41px>五、培训费用</p><p style=margin-top:4px;line-height:41px><span style=letter-spacing: 0px;>培训费用为 </span>1998 <span style=letter-spacing: 0px;>元</span>/人（不含住宿费<span style=letter-spacing: -11px;>）</span>。</p><p style=margin-top:2px;line-height:41px>六、报名方式</p><p style=margin-top:1px;margin-right:44px;margin-bottom:><span style=letter-spacing:>请参加培训人员登陆网址：</span><a href=http://t.cn/RcxJdEM><span style=font-family:&#39;Times>http://t.cn/RcxJdEM</span></a><span style=letter-spacing:-0>（</span>需区分大小写）<span style=letter-spacing:-0>或 </span><span style=font-family:&#39;Times>http://ballot.sacinfo.org.cn:8080/meeting_reply/px </span>在线填写参会回执，报名截止日期为 <span style=font-family:&#39;Times>9 </span><span style=letter-spacing:0>月 </span>16 <span style=letter-spacing:0>日。</span></p><p><br/></p><p>七、付款方式<br/></p><p style=margin-top:2px;margin-right:44px;margin-bottom:>1. 汇款方式：请于开班前将培训费汇到国家标准化管理委 员 会 标 准 信 息 中 心 ， 备 注 “ 培 训 费 <span style=letter-spacing:>”</span>， 并 邮 件</p><p style=margin-left:36px;line-height:36px><span style=letter-spacing:0>（</span><a href=mailto:spzxpxb@sina.com><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:0;text-underline:>s</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:0;text-underline:none>p</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:-0;text-underline:>z</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:0;text-underline:none>xp</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:-0;text-underline:>x</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:0;text-underline:none>b</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:0;text-underline:>@</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:-0;text-underline:none>s</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:0;text-underline:>i</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:0;text-underline:none>n</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:-0;text-underline:>a</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:0;text-underline:none>.</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:0;text-underline:>c</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:-0;text-underline:none>o</span><span style=color:windowtext;letter-spacing:-0;text-underline:>m</span></a>）告知汇款结果。</p><p style=margin-top:2px;margin-right:119px;margin-bottom:>开户名称：国家标准化管理委员会标准信息中心 汇款银行：工商银行北京北太平庄支行</p><p style=margin-left:83px;line-height:36px>汇款账号：0200010009200351961</p><p style=margin-left:83px;line-height:36px>2.现金方式：报到时交付（只接受现金，不能刷卡）</p><p style=line-height:41px>八、组织单位及联系方式主办方：</p><p style=line-height:36px>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;国家标准委标准信息中心（审评中心）</p><p style=line-height:36px>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;联系人：刁&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 晨&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 010-82261043&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 13910709584</p><p style=line-height:36px>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;何玉环&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 010-82261015&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 15801311606</p><p style=line-height:33px>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;承办方：</p><p style=line-height:37px>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;国家技术标准创新基地（重庆）</p><p style=line-height:37px>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;联系人：赵&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 明&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 023-88215838&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 13908353843</p><p style=line-height:37px>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;九、附件</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=line-height:><img src=http://www.cqbzjd.com/Public/ueditor/dialogs/attachment/fileTypeImages/icon_pdf.gif //><a style=font-size:12px; href=/ueditor/php/upload/file/20180822/1534931219432555.pdf title=通知-2018年第六期标准制修订全过程质量提升研修班通知.pdf>通知-2018年第六期标准制修订全过程质量提升研修班通知.pdf</a></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '6', null, '1534931428', '0', '2');

-- ----------------------------
-- Table structure for `sp_sysset`
